This present, I cannot say much of it, for there is not much said in it. However, be pleased to deign it your acceptance, if not for the offerer, yet for the oblations sake, (
   〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
) for it is a work holding forth such words as shall judge us all, even Judges,1 Thes. 5.13. Joh. 12.48. and all, at the last day. Now the Lord grant you may so pull down, and set up, so change, reform, and confirm; so purge and refine, that if it be possible, you may make a Coelum terrae, and so become your selves Rutilantia Sydera in seculo seculorum;
